<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date"> <xsl:param name="Name"/> <xsl:param name="DateFrom"/> <xsl:param name="DateTo"/> <xsl:param name="MustFinishBefore"/> <xsl:param name="Description"/> <xsl:param name="TimeEstimationHours"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ProjectTask"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ProjectTask"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="Name"><xsl:value-of select="$Name"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="DateFrom"><xsl:value-of select="concat($DateFrom,':00')"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="DateTo"><xsl:value-of select="concat($DateTo,':00')"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="MustFinishBefore"><xsl:value-of select="concat($MustFinishBefore,':00')"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="TimeEstimationHours"><xsl:value-of select="$TimeEstimationHours"/></xsl:attribute> <Description> <xsl:value-of select="$Description"/> </Description> <xsl:copy-of select="*[name() != 'Description']"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

<xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" xmlns:json='http://james.newtonking.com/projects/json' exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <xsl:apply-templates/> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="*"> <xsl:call-template name="copy"/> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template name="copy"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:for-each select="@*"> <xsl:attribute name="json:Array">true</xsl:attribute> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="name()='RecordUpdated' or name()='RecordCreated' or name()='Datum' or name()='TimeFinished' or name()='Date'" > <xsl:element name="{name()}"><xsl:value-of select="substring-before(., '+' )"/></xsl:element> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <xsl:element name="{name()}"><xsl:value-of select="."/></xsl:element> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:for-each> <xsl:apply-templates/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
